      "guest": "Sofia Coppola on",
      "films": [
        {
          "title": "Priscilla",
          "year": 2023,
          "note": "Coppola on finding an old '80s copy of the memoir, keeping a running list of questions for Priscilla Presley, building Graceland to scale in Toronto (William Eggleston photos as reference), casting Spaeny and Elordi, and the Dolly Parton needle drop that bookends Priscilla's arrival and departure."
        },
        {
